section.def:
berth
                                                (停泊) means to
                                    berth, moor, anchor or secure any vessel;

Director
                                                (處長) means the
                                    Director of Marine;

vehicle
                                                (車輛) means any
                                    vehicle intended or adapted for use on roads;

subparagraph.content:
the handling, inspection or weighing of cargo or cargo containers in
                        any public cargo working area, public water-front or excluded
                        water-front;
